\u1eddi con Ninh B&igrave;nh phong c\\u1ea3nh s\\u01a1n th\\u1ee7y k\\u1ef3 t&uacute;, nh\\u01b0ng c\\u0169ng ch&iacute;nh con ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi c\\u0169ng g&oacute;p ph\\u1ea7n t&ocirc;n vinh v&agrave; l&agrave;m \\u0111\\u1eb9p th&ecirc;m phong c\\u1ea3nh c\\u1ee7a t\\u1ea1o h&oacute;a. V\\u1edbi ki\\u1ebfn tr&uacute;c \\u0111\\u1ed3 s\\u1ed9, nguy nga, l\\u1ed9ng l\\u1eaby, nh\\u1eefng pho t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng c&oacute; n&eacute;t uy nghi, bao dung, ngh\\u1ec7 thu\\u1eadt ch\\u1ea1m kh\\u1eafc, \\u0111&uacute;c \\u0111\\u1ed3ng tinh t\\u1ebf, t&agrave;i t&igrave;nh c&ugrave;ng c\\u1ea3nh quan h&ugrave;ng v\\u0129, n&uacute;i g\\u1ed1i \\u0111\\u1ea7u s&ocirc;ng, m&acirc;y v\\u1eddn \\u0111\\u1ec9nh n&uacute;i, kh&ocirc;ng gian t&acirc;m linh thanh t\\u1ecbnh bao tr&ugrave;m khi\\u1ebfn m\\u1ed7i khi b\\u01b0\\u1edbc ch&acirc;n \\u0111\\u1ebfn \\u0111&acirc;y, ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi th\\u01b0 th&aacute;i, l&ograve;ng s&aacute;ng, t&acirc;m t\\u1ecbnh. \\u0110\\u1ebfn v\\u1edbi B&aacute;i \\u0110&iacute;nh &ndash; ng&ocirc;i ch&ugrave;a l\\u1edbn nh\\u1ea5t Vi\\u1ec7t Nam, du kh&aacute;ch s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c chi&ecirc;m b&aacute;i hai khu ch&ugrave;a l&agrave; T&acirc;n T\\u1ef1 v&agrave; C\\u1ed5 T\\u1ef1 c&ugrave;ng c&aacute;c c\\u1ea3nh \\u0111i\\u1ec3m ch&iacute;nh nh\\u01b0 h&agrave;nh lang La H&aacute;n d&agrave;i nh\\u1ea5t Vi\\u1ec7t Nam, B\\u1ea3o Th&aacute;p th\\u1edd x&aacute; l\\u1ee3i Ph\\u1eadt t\\u1eeb \\u1ea4n \\u0110\\u1ed9 v&agrave; Mi\\u1ebfn \\u0110i\\u1ec7n,&hellip;.<br \\/>11h30: \\u0110o&agrave;n \\u0103n tr\\u01b0a t\\u1ea1i nh&agrave; h&agrave;ng v&agrave; ngh\\u1ec9 ng\\u01a1i t\\u1ea1i Ninh B&igrave;nh.<br \\/>\\r\\n<p>13h30: \\u0110o&agrave;n ti\\u1ebfp t\\u1ee5c di chuy\\u1ec3n \\u0111\\u1ebfn khu th\\u1eafng c\\u1ea3nh Tr&agrave;ng An.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>14h: \\u0110o&agrave;n b\\u1eaft \\u0111\\u1ea7u th\\u0103m khu di t&iacute;chTr&agrave;ng An b\\u1eb1ng \\u0111&ograve;.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>To&agrave;n c\\u1ea3nh khu sinh