=\\\"787\\\">Tr\\u01b0a \\u0111\\u1ebfn ga Lhasa, xe v&agrave; h\\u01b0\\u1edbng d\\u1eabn \\u0111\\u1ecba ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng \\u0111&oacute;n \\u0111o&agrave;n v\\u1ec1 th\\u1ee7 ph\\u1ee7 T&acirc;y T\\u1ea1ng &ndash; Lhasa c\\u0169ng l&agrave; th&agrave;nh ph\\u1ed1 l\\u1edbn nh\\u1ea5t c\\u1ee7a \\u0111\\u1eb7c khu t\\u1ef1 tr\\u1ecb T&acirc;y T\\u1ea1ng v&agrave; l&agrave; th&aacute;nh \\u0111\\u1ecba Ph\\u1eadt Gi&aacute;o Trung Qu\\u1ed1c, tr&ecirc;n \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng v\\u1ec1 th&agrave;nh ph\\u1ed1 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ng\\u1eafm to&agrave;n c\\u1ea3nh cu\\u1ed9c s\\u1ed1ng c\\u1ee7a d&acirc;n t\\u1ed9c T\\u1ea1ng. <br \\/>Chi\\u1ec1u ngh\\u1ec9 ng\\u01a1i t\\u1ef1 do \\u0111\\u1ec3 th&iacute;ch h\\u1ee3p v\\u1edbi kh&iacute; h\\u1eadu v&ugrave;ng cao nguy&ecirc;n (\\u0111&acirc;y l&agrave; \\u0111i\\u1ec1u v&ocirc; c&ugrave;ng quan tr\\u1ecdng v&igrave; n\\u1ebfu kh&ocirc;ng \\u0111\\u1ec3 th\\u1eddi gian th&iacute;ch nghi kh&aacute;ch s\\u1ebd g\\u1eb7p ph\\u1ea3i c&aacute;c hi\\u1ec7n t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng th\\u01b0\\u1eddng c&oacute; nh\\u01b0 \\u0111au \\u0111\\u1ea7u, ch&oacute;ng m\\u1eb7t bu\\u1ed3n n&ocirc;n do thi\\u1ebfu oxy&hellip;) v&agrave; c&ugrave;ng nhau tham d\\u1ef1 bu\\u1ed5i giao l\\u01b0u h\\u1ed9i ng\\u1ed9 do Diamondtour s\\u1eafp x\\u1ebfp. \\u0110\\u01b0\\u1ee3c nghe gi\\u1edbi thi\\u1ec7u t\\u1ed5ng quan ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr&igrave;nh \\u0111\\u1ec3 qu&yacute; v\\u1ecb c&oacute; \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c m\\u1ed9t c\\u1ea3m quan t\\u1ed5ng th\\u1ec3 v\\u1ec1 l\\u1ecbch s\\u1eed, t&ocirc;n gi&aacute;o, con ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi T&acirc;y T\\u1ea1ng - \\u0111&acirc;y nh\\u01b0 m\\u1ed9t m&oacute;n qu&agrave; t\\u1eb7ng qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch nh&acirc;n ng&agrave;y \\u0111\\u1ea7u \\u0111\\u1ebfn T&acirc;y T\\u1ea1ng. \\u0102n t\\u1ed1i, ngh\\u1ec9 \\u0111&ecirc;m t\\u1ea1i Lhasa.<\\/td>\\r\\n<\\/tr>\\r\\n<\\/tbody>\\r\\n<\\/table>\",\"<table width=\\\"787\\\">\\r\\n<tbody>\\r\\n<tr>\\r\\n<td colspan=\\\"2\\\" width=\\\"787\\\">S&aacute;ng \\u0111o&agrave;n th\\u0103m cung \\u0111i\\u1ec7n Potala &ndash; cung \\u0111i\\u1ec7n n\\u1eb1m \\u1edf v\\u1ecb tr&iacute; cao nh\\u1ea5t th\\u1ebf gi\\u1edbi \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c x&acirc;y d\\u1ef1ng \\u1edf \\u0111\\u1ed9 cao h\\u01a1n 3.600 m. \\u0110o&agrave;n th\\u0103m hai t\\u1ea7ng l\\u1ea7u ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; Portrang Karpo (B\\u1ea1ch Cung) v&agrave; Portrang Marpo (H\\u1ed3ng Cung).<br \\/>\\u0102n tr\\u01b0a sau \\u0111&oacute; \\u0111o&agrave;n th\\u0103m ch&ugrave;a \\u0110\\u1ea1i Chi&ecirc;u, m\\u1ed9t trong nh\\u1eefng ng&ocirc;i ch&ugrave;a linh thi&ecirc;ng nh\\u1ea5t v\\u1edbi Ph\\u1eadt gi&aacute;o T&acirc;y T\\u1ea1ng.<br \\/>\\u0110o&agrave;n t\\u1ef1 do mua s\\u1eafm t\\u1ea1i ch\\u1ee3 B&aacute;t gi&aacute;c cho \\u0111\\u1ebfn khi \\u0103n t\\u1ed1i, ngh\\u1ec9 \\u0111&ecirc;m t\\u1ea1i Lhasa.<\\/td>\\r\\n<\\/tr>\\r\\n<\\/tbody>\\r\\n<\\/table>\",\"<table width=\\\"787\\\">\\r\\n<tbody>\\r\\n<tr>\\r\\n<td colspan=\\\"2\\\" width=\\\"787\\\">Bu\\u1ed5i s&aacute;ng, qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u1ebfn th\\u0103m tu vi\\u1ec7n Drepung- tu vi\\u1ec7n h\\u01a1n 600 n\\u0103m tu\\u1ed5i linh thi&ecirc;ng b\\u1eadc nh\\u1ea5t T&acirc;y T\\u1ea1ng<br \\/>V&agrave;o ng&agrave;y n&agrave;y, qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c chi&ecirc;m ng\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng nghi l\\u1ec5 &ldquo;t\\u1eafm Ph\\u1eadt trong &aacute;nh m\\u1eb7t tr\\u1eddi&rdquo; (nghi l\\u1ec5 tr\\u1ea3i b\\u1ee9c tranh Thangka kh\\u1ed5ng l\\u1ed3- b\\u1ee9c tranh \\u0111\\u1ee9c Ph\\u1eadt th&iacute;ch ca m&acirc;u ni r\\u1ed9ng h\\u01a1n 500m2 d\\u1ea7n m\\u1edf tr&ecirc;n l\\u01b0ng \\u0111\\u1ed3i c\\u1ee7a tu vi\\u1ec7n).<br \\/>Norbulingka l&agrave; cung \\u0111i\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ec3 c&aacute;c \\u0110\\u1ee9c \\u0110\\u1ea1i Lai L\\u1ea1t Ma l&agrave;m vi\\u1ec7c v&agrave;o m&ugrave;a h&egrave;, x&acirc;y d\\u1ef1ng v&agrave;o n\\u0103m 1751, n\\u01a1i \\u0111&acirc;y mang \\u0111\\u1eadm c\\u1ea5u tr&uacute;c v\\u01b0\\u1eddn hoa \\u0111i\\u1ec3n h&igrave;nh c\\u1ee7a T&acirc;y T\\u1ea1ng. <br \\/>Bu\\u1ed5i chi\\u1ec1u, qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u1ebfn th\\u0103m tu vi\\u1ec7n Sera, m\\u1ed9t trong ba tu vi\\u1ec7n l\\u1edbn c\\u1ee7a T&acirc;y T\\u1ea1ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c th&agrave;nh l\\u1eadp v&agrave;o n\\u0103m 1419, \\u0111\\u1ea1i di\\u1ec7n cho d&ograve;ng Gelugpa &ndash; ph&aacute;i C&aacute;ch L\\u1ed7. Tu vi\\u1ec7n g\\u1ed3m c&oacute; hai \\u0111\\u1ea1i h\\u1ecdc \\u0111\\u1ed9c l\\u1eadp Sera Je v&agrave; Sera Mey, v&agrave; tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng M\\u1eadt t&ocirc;ng Ngagpa Dratsang.<br \\/>V&agrave;o bu\\u1ed5i t\\u1ed1i, qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch c&oacute; c\\u01a1 h\\u1ed9i giao l\\u01b0u v\\u0103n ho&aacute; \\u1ea9m th\\u1ef1c, n\\u1ea5u \\u0103n trong c&aacute;c gia \\u0111&igrave;nh \\u0111\\u1ecba ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng T&acirc;y T\\u1ea1ng.<\\/td>\\r\\n<\\/tr>\\r\\n<\\/tbody>\\r\\n<\\/table>\",\"<table width=\\\"787\\\">\\r\\n<tbody>\\r\\n<tr>\\r\\n<td colspan=\\\"2\\\" width=\\\"787\\\">Sau b\\u1eefa s&aacute;ng, \\u0111o&agrave;n l&ecirc;n xe \\u0111i Shigatse &ndash; th&agrave;nh ph\\u1ed1 l\\u1edbn th\\u1ee9 2 c\\u1ee7a ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi T&acirc;y T\\u1ea1ng, kho\\u1ea3ng c&aacute;ch 320km. Tr&ecirc;n \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng \\u0111o&agrave;n gh&eacute; th\\u0103m v&agrave; chi&ecirc;m ng\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng th&aacute;nh h\\u1ed3 Yamdrok hay D\\u01b0\\u01a1ng Th&aacute;nh H\\u1ed3 &ndash; m\\u1ed9t trong 3 th&aacute;nh h\\u1ed3 l\\u1edbn nh\\u1ea5t v&agrave; \\u0111\\u1eb9p nh\\u1ea5t c\\u1ee7a T&acirc;y T\\u1ea1ng. T\\u1ea1i \\u0111&acirc;y Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch c&oacute; th\\u1ec3 t\\u1ef1 do ch\\u1ee5p \\u1ea3nh v\\u1edbi Yak ho\\u1eb7c Ngao T\\u1ea1ng (chi ph&iacute; t\\u1ef1 t&uacute;c). <br \\/>\\u0102n tr\\u01b0a sau \\u0111&oacute; tr&ecirc;n \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng \\u0111i Shigatse, \\u0111o&agrave;n gh&eacute; th\\u0103m tu vi\\u1ec7n Palkhor &ndash; m\\u1ed9t tu vi\\u1ec7n n\\u1ed5i ti\\u1ebfng v&igrave; \\u0111&acirc;y l&agrave; n\\u01a1i tu 